'''布萊恩·考克斯'''，[[英帝國司令勳章|CBE]]，[[皇家學會院士|FRS]]（{{lang-en|'''Brian Cox'''}}，{{bd|1968年|3月3日|catIdx=M}}），英国[[物理学家|物理学家]]， 他在[[曼彻斯特大学|曼彻斯特大学]]的{{link-en|曼彻斯特大学物理学和天文学院|School of Physics and Astronomy, University of Manchester|物理学和天文学院}}担任[[粒子物理学|粒子物理学]][[教授|教授]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://inspirehep.net/author/profile/B.E.Cox.1 |title=Cox, Brian E. - Profile - INSPIRE-HEP |accessdate=2017-12-07 |archive-date=2018-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023055153/https://inspirehep.net/author/profile/B.E.Cox.1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/brian.cox/ |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-12-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030075809/http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/brian.cox |archivedate=2015-10-30  }}</ref> 他因为主持过一系列科学类电视节目而为大众熟知，特别是他主持过的奇迹系列节目（''Wonders of…''系列）。<ref name="imdb">{{IMDb name|2207118|Professor Brian Cox}}</ref><ref name=bbcox>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/search/?q=brian%20cox |title=BBC - Search results for brian cox |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2017-12-07 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924015549/https://www.bbc.co.uk/search?q=brian%20cox |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title='Brian Cox effect' leads to surge in demand for physics |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/universityeducation/9793822/Brian-Cox-effect-leads-to-surge-in-demand-for-physics.html |newspaper=The Daily Telegraph |date=2013-01-30 |accessdate=2013-01-30 |archive-date=2013-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130129212045/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/universityeducation/9793822/Brian-Cox-effect-leads-to-surge-in-demand-for-physics.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他还著有[[科学普及|大众科普]]书籍，例如[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Why_Does_E%3Dmc%C2%B2%3F 《为什么E=mc²?相对论普及读本》] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Why_Does_E%3Dmc%C2%B2%3F |date=20170408102323 }}以及{{link-en|《科学可以这样看丛书：量子宇宙》|The Quantum Universe}}，他编写或参与编写了超过950本科学出版物。<ref name="Manchester">{{cite web |title=Prof Brian Cox - publications |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913171741/http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/brian.cox/publications |archive-date=2016-09-13 |url=http://www.manchester.ac.uk/research/brian.cox/publications |publisher=University of Manchester |dead-url=yes |accessdate=2016-08-18}}</ref>

考克斯被[[戴維·阿滕伯勒|大卫•阿滕伯勒]]和[[帕特里克·穆爾|帕特里克•穆尔]]称作[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]（BBC）科学类节目主持人的最佳继承者。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Sir David Attenborough says he would like to pass on the baton to Professor Brian Cox |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/9837922/Sir-David-Attenborough-says-he-would-like-to-pass-on-the-baton-to-Professor-Brian-Cox.html |newspaper=The Daily Telegraph |date=2013-01-30 |accessdate=2013-01-30 |archive-date=2013-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130203135008/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/9837922/Sir-David-Attenborough-says-he-would-like-to-pass-on-the-baton-to-Professor-Brian-Cox.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Brian Cox? He's no astronomer! Patrick Moore turns his telescope on the young pretender - and concedes he's really rather good (for an ex-rock star) |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2090883/Brian-Cox-Hes-astronomer-Patrick-Moore-turns-telescope-young-pretender--concedes-hes-really-good-ex-rock-star.html |newspaper=Daily Mail |date=2012-01-24 |accessdate=2013-01-30 |archive-date=2014-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924042454/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2090883/Brian-Cox-Hes-astronomer-Patrick-Moore-turns-telescope-young-pretender--concedes-hes-really-good-ex-rock-star.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在开始他学术职业生涯之前，考克斯曾在[[D:Ream乐队|D:Ream乐队]]和{{link-en|Dare乐队|Dare (band)}}担任[[键盘手|键盘手]]。他作为英国广播公司的主持人所获得的年收入约为£250,000 - £299,999。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-40653861|title=BBC pay: How much do its stars earn?|date=2017-07-19|publisher=|via=www.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2017-12-07|archive-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725203927/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-40653861|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早年生活和教育==
[[File:Prof_Brian_Cox.jpg|thumb]]
1968年3月3日，考克斯出生在{{link-en|皇家奥尔德姆医院|Royal Oldham Hospital}}。从1971年开始，他生活在[[奧爾德姆|奥尔德姆]]{{link-en|查德顿|Chadderton}}。<ref name=whoswho>{{Who's Who |surname=COX |othernames=Prof. Brian Edward |id=U261949 |volume=2016 |edition=online [[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]] |location=Oxford}} {{subscription required}}</ref><ref name="birthdate">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2008/sep/14/cern.particlephysics |title=Putting the fizz into physics |first=David |last=Smith |work=The Observer |date=2008-09-14 |accessdate=2008-09-14 |location=London |archive-date=2019-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501103640/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2008/sep/14/cern.particlephysics |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Human Universe - 4. A Place in Space and Time</ref> 他的父母在[[約克郡銀行|约克郡银行]]工作，父亲和母亲在同一家支行工作，母亲是那里的银行柜员，父亲则是中层管理人员。<ref>{{Cite news |title=The Times Saturday September 12th 2015 Weekend section |access-date=|via=}}</ref> 据他回忆，自己在[[奧爾德姆|奥尔德姆]]度过了快乐的童年，小时候的他喜欢[[舞蹈|舞蹈]]，[[体操|体操]]，他还是个[[飞机摄影|飞机迷]]和[[巴士迷|巴士迷]]。在1979年和1986年之间，他在奥尔德姆休姆文法学校上学，那是一所私立学校。<ref name=whoswho/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hulme-grammar.oldham.sch.uk/alumni |title=Oldham Hulme Grammar Alumni |website= |publisher=Oldham Hulme Grammar School |archivedate=2013-12-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6LxKS816M?url=http://www.hulme-grammar.oldham.sch.uk/alumni/ |deadurl=yes  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.hulme-grammar.oldham.sch.uk/news/view/congratulations_to_professor_brian_cox_obe |title=Congratulations to Professor Brian Cox OBE |date=2010-06-17 |accessdate=2011-03-03 |publisher=Oldham Hulme Grammar School website |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110308204040/http://www.hulme-grammar.oldham.sch.uk/news/view/congratulations_to_professor_brian_cox_obe |archivedate=2011-03-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Alumni |url=http://www.hulme-grammar.oldham.sch.uk/common/alumni_gen.php |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130707075646/http://www.hulme-grammar.oldham.sch.uk/common/alumni_gen.php |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2013-07-07 |work=Oldham Hulme Grammar School website |publisher=[[Hulme_Grammar_School|Oldham Hulme Grammar School]] |accessdate=2013-05-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-12344973 |title=Brian Cox: Science is not 'dominated by old men' |publisher=BBC News |date=2011-02-02 |accessdate=2011-03-03 |archive-date=2011-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110225213301/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-12344973 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在很多次接受采访的时候，以及《宇宙的奇迹》一期节目中，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00zdhtg |title=BBC Two Programmes – Wonders of the Universe |accessdate=2011-03-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110402065141/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00zdhtg |archivedate=2011-04-02  }}</ref> 考克斯说自己12岁那年读了[[卡尔·萨根|卡尔•萨根]]写的{{link-en|《宇宙》|Cosmos_(Carl_Sagan_book)}}，这本书对他启发很大，激励他成为物理学家。<ref name="birthdate"/> 他在[[強納森·羅斯秀|强纳森•罗斯秀]]的一期节目中坦言自己[[普通教育高级程度证书|A-level考试]]中的数学成绩很不好，他说：“我数学成绩是D……我那时候数学真的很差……后来我知道了，想要数学好就得多练习。”<ref>{{cite news |title=Jonathan Ross welcomes Matt Smith to his Friday night show |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2010/03_march/26/ross.shtml |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |accessdate=2012-10-04 |date=2010-03-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421200522/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2010/03_march/26/ross.shtml |archivedate=2014-04-21  }}</ref>

===音乐===
20世纪80年代和90年代早期，考克斯在摇滚乐队{{link-en|Dare乐队|Dare (band)}}担任[[键盘手|键盘手]]。<ref>{{cite news |title=A Life in the Day: Dr Brian Cox |url=http://women.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/women/the_way_we_live/article3403949.ece |newspaper=[[The_Times|The Times]] |date=2008-02-24 |accessdate=2011-01-06 |location=London |first1=Philippe |last1=Naughton |first2=Miles |last2=Costello |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615172946/http://women.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/women/the_way_we_live/article3403949.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref> Dare乐队发行过两张考克斯参与制作的专辑，分别是1988年发行的''Out of the Silence''以及1991年发行的''Blood from Stone''。之后他加入了[[D:Ream乐队|D:Ream乐队]]，<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2010/apr/04/brian-cox-observer-profile |title=Brian Cox: The man with the stars in his eyes |author=Caspar Llewellyn Smith |newspaper=[[The_Observer|The Observer]] |date=2010-04-04 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |location=London |archive-date=2014-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141107041905/http://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2010/apr/04/brian-cox-observer-profile |dead-url=no }}</ref> D:Ream乐队有好几首歌都登上过[[英國單曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]，其中包括登上过榜首的''{{link-en|Things Can Only Get Better|Things_Can_Only_Get_Better_(D:Ream_song)}}''。<ref>[http://www.everyhit.co.uk/ UK top 40 hit database] {{Wayback|url=http://www.everyhit.co.uk/ |date=20180918234716 }}, EveryHit.co.uk (search result for ''D:Ream''), done 6 September 2008</ref> 后来这首歌被[[新工党|新工党]]用作选举的助选歌曲，但是考克斯并没有参与这首歌的录制。

===高等教育===
考克斯在发展音乐事业的同时进入了[[曼彻斯特大学|曼彻斯特大学]]学习[[物理学|物理学]]。他获得了[[理學士|理学学士]]学位，{{link-en|一等荣誉|British_undergraduate_degree_classification#First-class_honours}}，以及物理学[[研究碩士|研究硕士]]学位。1997年D:Ream乐队解散后，他完成了在[[曼彻斯特大学|曼彻斯特大学]]的学习，并获得了[[粒子物理學|高能粒子物理学]]的[[哲学博士|哲学博士]]学位。<ref name="coxphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Brian Edward |last=Cox |title=Double diffraction dissociation at large momentum transfer |publisher=University of Manchester |year=1998 |url=http://www-h1.desy.de/psfiles/theses/h1th-679.pdf |website=desy.de |oclc=644443338 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114112943/http://www-h1.desy.de/psfiles/theses/h1th-679.pdf |archivedate=2014-11-14  }} {{EThOS|uk.bl.ethos.675409}}</ref> 他的论文''Double Diffraction Dissociation at Large Momentum Transfer'',<ref name="coxphd"/> 是在{{link-en|羅賓·馬歇爾|Robin Marshall}}的指导下完成的，<ref name="coxphd"/><ref>{{Who's Who |surname=Marshall |othernames=Prof. Robin |id=U26756 |volume=2015 |edition=online [[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]}} {{subscription required}}</ref> 并且是基于他曾开展过的[[H1|H1]]实验，该实验是关于{{link-en|HERA粒子加速器|HERA (particle accelerator)}},<ref name="coxphd"/><ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Cox |first1=B. |authorlink1=Brian Cox (physicist) |title=A review of forward proton tagging at 420m at the LHC, and relevant results from the Tevatron and HERA |doi=10.1063/1.1896693 |volume=753 |pages=103–111 |year=2005 |arxiv=hep-ph/0409144 }}</ref>  实验地点为[[德国|德国]][[汉堡|汉堡]]的[[德國電子加速器|德国电子同步加速器]]研究所。<ref>[http://www.apolloschildren.com:16080/brian/ Professor Brian Cox] 8 {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123123111/http://www.apolloschildren.com:16080/brian/ |date=2013-01-23 }}</ref>

==职业==
===研究===
考克斯是[[曼彻斯特大学|曼彻斯特大学]]的[[高能物理|高能物理]]组成员，他还参与了[[大型強子對撞機|大型强子对撞机]]（LHC）的[[超環面儀器|超环面仪器]]实验，<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Cox |first1=B. |authorlink1=Brian Cox (physicist) |last2=Forshaw |first2=J. |authorlink2=Jeff Forshaw|last3=Lee |first3=J. |last4=Monk |first4=J. |last5=Pilaftsis |first5=A. |title=Observing a light CP-violating Higgs boson in diffraction |doi=10.1103/PhysRevD.68.075004 |journal=Physical Review D |volume=68 |issue=7 |year=2003 |arxiv=hep-ph/0303206 |bibcode=2003PhRvD..68g5004C}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Cox |first1=B. |authorlink1=Brian Cox (physicist) |last2=Forshaw |first2=J.|authorlink2=Jeff Forshaw|last3=Heinemann |first3=B. |title=Double diffractive higgs and di-photon production at the Tevatron and LHC |doi=10.1016/S0370-2693(02)02144-5 |journal=Physics Letters B |volume=540 |issue=3–4 |pages=263–268 |year=2002 |arxiv=hep-ph/0110173 |bibcode=2002PhLB..540..263C}}</ref> 实验地点位于[[瑞士|瑞士]][[日内瓦|日内瓦]]近郊的[[歐洲核子研究組織|欧洲核子研究中心]]。<ref name=ted>{{TED speaker|brian_cox}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_on_cern_s_supercollider |title=Brian Cox: CERN's supercollider - TED Talk |author=Brian Cox |publisher=ted.com |accessdate=2017-12-11 |archive-date=2017-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127100344/https://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_on_cern_s_supercollider |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_what_went_wrong_at_the_lhc |title=Brian Cox: What went wrong at the LHC - TED Talk |author=Brian Cox |publisher=ted.com |accessdate=2017-12-11 |archive-date=2017-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917051920/https://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_what_went_wrong_at_the_lhc |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_why_we_need_the_explorers |title=Brian Cox: Why we need the explorers - TED Talk |author=Brian Cox |publisher=ted.com |accessdate=2017-12-11 |archive-date=2018-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109104900/https://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_why_we_need_the_explorers |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他参与的{{link-en|FP420|FP420 experiment}}[[研究開發|研发]]实验项目是个国际合作项目，该项目需要通过在距离主要实验的相互作用点420米的位置安装额外的且更小的[[粒子探测器|粒子探测器]]，达到升级超环面仪器（ATLAS）和[[紧凑μ子线圈|紧凑μ子线圈]]（CMS）<ref>{{Cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.physletb.2012.08.021 |title=Observation of a new boson at a mass of 125 GeV with the CMS experiment at the LHC |journal=Physics Letters B |volume=716 |page=30 |year=2012 |last1=Chatrchyan |first1=S. |last2=Khachatryan |first2=V. |last3=Sirunyan |first3=A. M. |last4=Tumasyan |first4=A. |last5=Adam |first5=W. |last6=Aguilo |first6=E. |last7=Bergauer |first7=T. |last8=Dragicevic |first8=M. |last9=Erö |first9=J. |last10=Fabjan |first10=C. |last11=Friedl |first11=M. |last12=Frühwirth |first12=R. |last13=Ghete |first13=V. M. |last14=Hammer |first14=J. |last15=Hoch |first15=M. |last16=Hörmann |first16=N. |last17=Hrubec |first17=J. |last18=Jeitler |first18=M. |last19=Kiesenhofer |first19=W. |last20=Knünz |first20=V. |last21=Krammer |first21=M. |last22=Krätschmer |first22=I. |last23=Liko |first23=D. |last24=Majerotto |first24=W. |last25=Mikulec |first25=I. |last26=Pernicka |first26=M. |last27=Rahbaran |first27=B. |last28=Rohringer |first28=C. |last29=Rohringer |first29=H. |last30=Schöfbeck |first30=R. |display-authors=29|arxiv=1207.7235 |bibcode=2012PhLB..716...30C }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |doi=10.1103/PhysRevD.65.096014 |title=WW scattering at the CERN LHC |journal=[[Physical_Review|Physical Review]] D |volume=65 |issue=9 |year=2002 |last1=Butterworth |first1=J. M. |authorlink1=Jon Butterworth|last2=Cox |first2=B. E. |authorlink2=Brian Cox (physicist) |last3=Forshaw |first3=J. R. |authorlink3=Jeff Forshaw|arxiv=hep-ph/0201098|bibcode=2002PhRvD..65i6014B }}</ref> 的目的。<ref>FP420 R&D Project, ''[http://www.fp420.com/ FP420] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727213454/http://www.fp420.com/ |date=2009-07-27 }},'' 16 October 2007. Retrieved 5 April 2011</ref><ref name="scopus">{{Scopus id}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://arxiv.org/find/hep-ph/1/au:+Cox_B/0/1/0/all/0/1|title=arXiv.org Search|publisher=arxiv.org|accessdate=2017-12-11|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626220545/https://arxiv.org/find/hep-ph/1/au:+Cox_B/0/1/0/all/0/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=inspirehep>{{cite web|url=http://inspirebeta.net/search?ln=en&p=brian+cox&f=author|title=brian cox - Search Results - INSPIRE-HEP|publisher=inspirebeta.net|access-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130222122859/http://inspirebeta.net/search?ln=en&p=brian+cox&f=author|archive-date=2013-02-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

