><ref name="jamesphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=James William |last=Monk |title=Study of central exclusive production |publisher=University of Manchester |year=2006 |url=http://www.hep.man.ac.uk/u/forshaw/monk.pdf |access-date=2017-12-11 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626220550/http://www.hep.man.ac.uk/u/forshaw/monk.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="irinaphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Irina Naskova |last=Nasteva |title=Exclusive Higgs production and decay to WW(*) at the LHC and semiconductor tracker studies for the ATLAS detector |publisher=University of Manchester |year=2006 |url=http://man-fe.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?vid=MU_VU1&doc=44MAN_ALMA_DS21194931120001631 |access-date=2017-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211213534/http://man-fe.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?vid=MU_VU1&doc=44MAN_ALMA_DS21194931120001631 |archive-date=2017-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="andresphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Andres Felipe |last=Osorio Oliveros |title=WW scattering studies for a future linear collider |publisher=University of Manchester |year=2006 |url=http://man-fe.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?vid=MU_VU1&doc=44MAN_ALMA_DS21195660680001631 |access-date=2017-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117041201/http://man-fe.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?vid=MU_VU1&doc=44MAN_ALMA_DS21195660680001631 |archive-date=2016-01-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="pilkingtonphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Andrew Denis |last=Pilkington |title=Central exclusive production in TeV energies |publisher=University of Manchester |year=2006 |url=http://man-fe.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?vid=MU_VU1&doc=44MAN_ALMA_DS21167659030001631 |access-date=2017-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211161037/http://man-fe.hosted.exlibrisgroup.com/primo_library/libweb/action/display.do?vid=MU_VU1&doc=44MAN_ALMA_DS21167659030001631 |archive-date=2017-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===广播电视===
[[File:Professor_Brian_Cox_at_the_Science_Foo_Camp_--_11_August_2008.jpg|thumb]]
考克斯上过很多[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的广播节目和电视节目，<ref name="imdb"/><ref name=eden>{{cite web |url=http://eden.uktv.co.uk/people/brian-cox/ |title=Prof Brian Cox |publisher=uktv.co.uk |accessdate=2017-12-12 |archive-date=2017-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823210917/https://eden.uktv.co.uk/people/brian-cox/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 包括《在爱因斯坦的阴影下》''In Einstein's Shadow,''<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio4/science/ineinsteinsshadow.shtml |title=In Einstein's shadow |publisher=BBC |date=January 2005 |accessdate=2008-09-06 |archive-date=2008-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080628011236/http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio4/science/ineinsteinsshadow.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[地平线_(英国纪录片)|BBC地平线系列]]，<ref>Sue Rider Management, [http://www.sueridermanagement.co.uk/presenters/BrianCox/briancox.htm Professor Brian Cox] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sueridermanagement.co.uk/presenters/BrianCox/briancox.htm |date=20180203212836 }}. Retrieved 6 September 2008</ref> (《六十亿美元的实验》（"The Six Billion Dollar Experiment"）, 《重力错乱》（"What on Earth is Wrong with Gravity?"）, 《时空谜团》（"Do You Know What Time It Is?"）, 以及《人造恒星》（"Can we Make a Star on Earth?"）) ，他还为改版后的BBC教育资源网站{{link-en|Bitesize|Bitesize}}做过配音。2010年年初，他主持过[[英国广播公司第二台|英国广播公司第二台]]的电视节目{{link-en|《太阳系的奇迹》|Wonders of the Solar System}}，该节目共5集。接着又从2011年3月6日开始，主持了{{link-en|《宇宙的奇迹》|Wonders of the Universe}}，该节目共4集。<ref>''[http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00qyxfb Wonders of the Solar System] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00qyxfb |date=20171204150026 }}''. Retrieved 4 April 2010</ref>  2013年播出的《[[生命的奇迹|生命的奇迹]]》也由考克斯主持，他称这个节目为“一个物理学家对生命/博物学的看法和感悟”。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2011/mar/24/brian-cox-wonders-universe?commentpage=8#comment-10089245 |location=London |work=The Guardian |title=Brian Cox answers your questions about life, the universe and everything |date=2011-03-24 |accessdate=2017-12-13 |archive-date=2017-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213204421/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2011/mar/24/brian-cox-wonders-universe?commentpage=8#comment-10089245 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他参与过主持{{link-en|英国广播公司儿童频道|CBBC}}的节目''Space Hoppers''，并且作为客串嘉宾参演过儿童喜剧''{{link-en|Dani's House|Dani's House}}''。<ref>''[http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00rhdfn Space Hoppers] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00rhdfn |date=20180803155949 }}''. Retrieved 4 April 2010</ref>

考克斯还主持过BBC的纪录片《科学英国》''Science Britannica''（共3集），片中他带领观众纵览英国科学家在过去的350年里所作出的贡献，并探索了英国科学与英国民众的科学观之间的联系。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01d56dn |accessdate=2014-08-06 |title=Science Britannica |publisher=BBC |archive-date=2014-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112060832/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01d56dn |dead-url=no }}</ref>

英国广播公司第二台指派考克斯担任{{link-en|《观星指南》|Stargazing Live}}节目的主持人，《观星指南》是一档天文主题的电视直播节目，第一季于2011年1月在电视上直播，连续三天播完。该节目由考克斯和物理学家出身的喜剧明星[[达拉·奥布莱恩|达拉·奥布莱恩]]共同主持，脱口秀节目主持人[[强纳森·罗斯|强纳森·罗斯]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/commissioning/ross-returns-to-bbc-for-stargazing-series/5020981.article |title=Ross returns to BBC for ''Stargazing'' series |last=Neilan |first=Catherine |work=[[Broadcast_(magazine)|Broadcast]] |date=2010-11-25 |accessdate=2010-11-25 |archive-date=2011-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110316171709/http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/commissioning/ross-returns-to-bbc-for-stargazing-series/5020981.article |dead-url=no }}</ref> 也客串了这个节目。节目一经播出，就在[[英国|英国]]上下引发了一场天文热潮。第二季和第三季《观星指南》分别于2012年1月和2013年1月播出，有各路明星作为嘉宾参与。 <ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/speeches/stories/nasse_materials.shtml |title=Speech by Saul Nassé, Controller of Learning |date=2010-09-27 |accessdate=2010-12-06 |archive-date=2010-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101202073234/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/speeches/stories/nasse_materials.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

从2009年11月开始，考克斯和喜剧明星{{link-en|罗宾·因斯|Robin Ince}}共同主持{{link-en|英国广播公司广播4台|BBC Radio 4}}的趣味科学节目''{{link-en|The Infinite Monkey Cage|The Infinite Monkey Cage}}''。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/radio4/2010/06/ |title=Live chat: science fiction vs science fact |first=Steve |last=Bowbrick |work=[[BBC_Radio_4|BBC Radio 4]] |date=2010-06-28 |accessdate=2010-07-06 |archive-date=2012-07-29 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120729130111/www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/radio4/2010/06/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 参加过这个广播节目的嘉宾有喜剧明星[[蒂姆·明钦|蒂姆·明钦]]，{{link-en|阿雷克谢·塞利|Alexei Sayle}}，达拉·奥布莱恩，以及一些科学家，例如BBC纪录片{{link-en|“奇妙的人类旅程”|The Incredible Human Journey}}的主演{{link-en|爱丽丝·罗伯茨|Alice Roberts}}，还有天体物理学家[[尼尔·德葛拉司·泰森|尼尔·德葛拉司·泰森]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b085tq49|title=The Infinite Monkey Cage Christmas Special, The Infinite Monkey Cage - BBC Radio 4|website=BBC|access-date=2017-11-02|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930075627/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b085tq49|dead-url=no}}</ref> 考克斯还参加过因斯的节目{{link-en|《给无神论者的九节课和颂歌》|Nine Lessons and Carols for Godless People}}（''Nine Lessons and Carols for Godless People''），他每周做客一次[[BBC_6_Music|英国广播公司广播6台音乐频率]]（BBC 6 Music）的《音乐早餐》（Breakfast Show）节目，该节目的主持是{{link-en|尚恩·基夫尼|Shaun Keaveny}}。考克斯还曾于2009年7月24日参加过一期{{link-en|罗伯特·卢埃林|Robert Llewellyn}}的播客节目{{link-en|《搭车旅行脱口秀》|Carpool (web series)}}。<ref>CarPool, ''[http://www.llewtube.com/ Brian Cox on CarPool] {{Wayback|url=http://www.llewtube.com/ |date=20090423114846 }},'' 24 July 2009. Retrieved 19 September 2009.</ref>

考克斯还多次现身在[[TED大会|TED大会]]，做过一些关于大型强子对撞机（LHC）和粒子物理学的演讲。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ted.com/speakers/brian_cox |title=Brian Cox |work=[[TED_(conference)|TED]] |accessdate=2011-01-06 |archive-date=2014-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315031128/http://www.ted.com/speakers/brian_cox |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_on_cern_s_supercollider |title=Brian Cox: CERN's supercollider |work=TED |date=March 2008 |accessdate=2014-07-07 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714172042/http://www.ted.com/talks/brian_cox_on_cern_s_supercollider |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2009年他登上了[[人物_(杂志)|《人物》]]杂志评选的全球最性感男性榜单。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://atlas.ch/news/2009/sexiest-physicist.html |title=ATLAS physicist voted sexiest in the world |first=Ceri |last=Perkins |work=[[ATLAS_experiment|ATLAS]] eNews |date=February 2009 |accessdate=2014-07-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723123307/http://atlas.ch/news/2009/sexiest-physicist.html |archivedate=2011-07-23  }}</ref> 考克斯的声音曾在2010年和2011年被分别收录在{{link-en|《科学交响曲》|Symphony of Science}}的''The Case for Mars''和''The Quantum World''两首歌当中。2010年11月他在位于[[科文特花园|科文特花园]]的[[苹果零售店|苹果零售店]]宣传自己新出的[[电子书|电子书]]，这些书是他当时一个新电视节目的配套书籍，考克斯在现场还回答了一些观众提的问题。<ref>[http://www.harpercollins.co.uk/about-harpercollins/Imprints/collins/Pages/Collins.aspx Landmark Apple Store Event for Professor Cox] {{Wayback|url=http://www.harpercollins.co.uk/about-harpercollins/Imprints/collins/Pages/Collins.aspx |date=20130331074719 }}, press release from [[HarperCollins|HarperCollins]], 24 November 2010. Retrieved 6 December 2010.</ref>

考克斯教授最廣為人知的是作為[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]的節目主持人，推動天文學和物理學等科目的普及。在90年代他是流行樂隊[[D:Ream|D:Ream]]的鋼琴手，因此亦被稱為「搖滾明星物理學家」（Rock Star Physicist）。

